{"word":"G2840 - κοινόω - koinóō - koy-no'-o - Call common","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κοινόω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">koinóō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">koy-no'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Call common</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தீட்டுப்படுத்து"},{"paragraph":"1. to make common"},{"paragraph":"2. to make unclean, render unhallowed, defile, profane"},{"paragraph":"3. to declare or count unclean"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2839 - κοινός - koinós - koy-nos'/2839\">G2839</a>; to <i>make</i> (or <i>consider</i>) <i>profane</i> (ceremonially): - call common, defile, pollute, unclean.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2839/2839\">G2839</a>, <a href=\"#/G2840/2840\">G2840</a>, <a href=\"#/G2841/2841\">G2841</a>, <a href=\"#/G2842/2842\">G2842</a>, <a href=\"#/G2843/2843\">G2843</a>, <a href=\"#/G2844/2844\">G2844</a>, <a href=\"#/G4790/4790\">G4790</a>, <a href=\"#/G4791/4791\">G4791</a>"}]}